snippet.title: Trojan (NES) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A playthrough of Capcom's 1987 NES game, Trojan.

I believe I got all of the secret items. I managed to not die and get both power ups, making the last boss kind of easy. Awesome game.

For my review with a screenshot gallery and the soundtrack, check out http://www.nintendocomplete.com/Trojan
____
No cheats were used during the recording of this video.
